parameters: \n<Nathaniel>It's good to be away from the team
and all their bickering, haha. Gets
annoying sometimes, am I right? Haha.
\n<Jackie>Come on Jess, I'm doing my best.
Give me a break, will ya'?
If there's ever been a time for you to
step up and finally act like you care
about me, your sister... it's now.
